    Definition of available output types that can be chosen for a blukii number on blukii Info Manager (https://manager.blukiiinfo.com).



    It will be returned by ResolveData.getOutputType()

    According to the OutputType the ResolveData is affected:
    • PDF: ResolveData.getUrl() returns an url of an PDF-File;
      ResolveData.getUrlExtra() returns an url of an audio file
      ResolveData.getPlainTextExtra() returns a translated text
    • YOUTUBE: ResolveData.getUrl() returns an url of a youtube video
    • VCARD: ResolveData.getUrl() returns an url of a VCARD file (*.vcf) or a VCARD syntax string
    • WIFI: ResolveData.getUrl() returns an url of a WIFI file (*.wifi) or a WIFI syntax text
    • HTML: ResolveData.getUrl() returns an url of a web site
    • MESSAGE: ResolveData.getUrl() returns a translated message text
